    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "（と、休んでいるうちに寝てしまって……）\n（そのまま朝になったのか……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（And I ended up falling asleep while resting…）\n（And I slept until morning…?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_03-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "すまない、泊めてもらった上に\n布団までかけてもらって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sorry‚ not only did you let me stay the night‚\nYou even put a blanket on me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
